{"tid":1630828,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"張相係2016年，但到依家都啱用","createTime":"2019-10-06T13:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"76af4b4e29de68f0cfcb2652e49509eee0753d97","tid":1630828,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6ouKcB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6ouKcB.jpg&h=6d167f2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d3d28afff35bcfa6621f58a648c9f770e7578f5","tid":1630828,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:50:34.000Z","msg":"《暴徒》<br />\n<br />\n香港地有很多智者，<br />\n明明對於非本地的反抗行為，<br />\n一律予以無限同情，<br />\n甚至落淚痛哭，<br />\n更質問旁人為什麼不關注這些事情。<br />\n<br />\n可是，<br />\n當這些事情出現於自己身處的城市，<br />\n他們卻開始變臉。<br />\n莫說同情與否，<br />\n不譴責「暴徒」已經算是「寬大為懷」。<br />\n<br />\n要說「暴徒」，<br />\n豈可不提孫文？<br />\n他正是一個典型的「暴徒」，<br />\n所發動的騷亂（現稱「起義」），<br />\n一律有組織、預謀，<br />\n而且目標是顛覆家天下的大一統帝國，<br />\n還勾結外國勢力。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼封建帝制好地地運作了幾千年，<br />\n無端白事要走向共和？<br />\n為什麼要廢止纏足？<br />\n為什麼要實現民主？<br />\n為什麼中國會變成咁？<br />\n你會不會提出這些問題？<br />\n<br />\n武昌起義、辛亥革命成功了，<br />\n「暴徒」孫文華麗轉身，<br />\n變成了「國父」，為國人所稱頌。<br />\n中山陵、中山紀念堂，<br />\n還有各地的紀念碑、紀念館、中山路，<br />\n都是紀念這位「暴徒」的豐功偉績。<br />\n香港西營盤海傍，<br />\n建有「中山紀念公園」，豎立銅像；<br />\n中環甘堂第也改建成孫中山紀念館，<br />\n對這位「暴徒」的地位予以肯定。<br />\n<br />\n好在他成功了，<br />\n否則在歷史上，<br />\n武昌起義變成「武昌之亂」，<br />\n辛亥革命則是「辛亥民變」，<br />\n他亦只能成為永遠的「暴徒」。<br />\n歷史就是由勝利者書寫的。<br />\n<br />\nMF<br />\n<br />\n#middlefingerhk<br />\nInstagram: middlefingerhk"},{"pid":"da3b17342c0cb3b48beebc842fd96824d355b902","tid":1630828,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:50:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MiddleFingerHK/photos/a.818489494841702/1127224840634831?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMiddleFingerHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.818489494841702%2F1127224840634831%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6ndC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=9da4ac10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/MiddleFingerHK/photos/a.818489494841702/1127224840634831?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"557d533e3b28cb2a28f29c3a459bf957bc8655f5","tid":1630828,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6b926d735beb0d358fd0a3f3ba41d121ada95f","tid":1630828,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}